Create a text file named requirements.txt
Copy and paste these into your text file that is stored inside your virtual environment's folder.

praw
regex
mysql
mysql-connector

open cmd line and cd into the folder containing your requirements.txt file

type pip install -r requirements.txt

this should install praw, regex,mysql, and my sql-connector.




